<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Panel de Administraci√≥n - MyZoo</title>

    {# Preconexi√≥n para mejor performance #}
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://unpkg.com">

    {# Hojas de estilo externas #}
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet"
            integrity="sha384-9ndCyUaIbzAi2FUVXJi0CjmCapSmO7SnpJef0486qhLnuZ2cdeRhO02iuK6FUUVM" crossorigin="anonymous">

    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css"
            integrity="sha512-iecdLmaskl7CVkqkXNQ/ZH/XLlvWZOJyj7Yy7tcenmpD1ypASozpmT/E0iPtmFIB46ZmdtAc9eNBvH0H/ZpiBw=="
            crossorigin="anonymous" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" />

    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/animate.css/4.1.1/animate.min.css"
            integrity="sha512-c42qTSw/wPZ3/5LBzD+Bw5fFbUJNUx3j+HaURHvzHpqEj8U7DnFE8gVxyfD5xXiz0MYmmOKdGy3q5mQjXUuRQ=="
            crossorigin="anonymous" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" />

    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://unpkg.com/leaflet@1.9.4/dist/leaflet.css"
            integrity="sha256-p4NxAoJBhIIN+hmNHrzRCf9tD/miZyoHS5obTRR9BMY="
            crossorigin="anonymous"/>

    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            padding: 0;
            margin: 0;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }

        .zoo-header {
            background-color: #4caf50;
            color: white;
            padding: 1rem;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .zoo-footer {
            background-color: #354f30;
            color: white;
            padding: 2rem 0;
            margin-top: auto;
        }

        .zoo-footer h5 {
            color: #f1c40f;
        }

        .zoo-footer a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #aab7b8;
        }

        .zoo-footer a:hover {
            color: #f1c40f;
        }

        .nav-item a {
            color: white;
        }

        .nav-item a:hover {
            color: #ffeb3b;
        }

        /* --- Estilos para el Panel de Administraci√≥n --- */
        .admin-main-container {
            display: flex;
            flex: 1;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }

        .admin-sidebar {
            width: 250px;
            background-color: #2c3e50;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            box-shadow: 2px 0 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }

        .admin-sidebar h2 {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            color: #ecf0f1;
        }

        .admin-sidebar nav ul {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .admin-sidebar nav ul li {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .admin-sidebar nav ul li a {
            display: block;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 12px 15px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, color 0.3s ease;
            font-weight: bold;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .admin-sidebar nav ul li a i {
            margin-right: 10px;
        }

        .admin-sidebar nav ul li a:hover,
        .admin-sidebar nav ul li a.active {
            background-color: #34495e;
            color: #f1c40f;
        }

        .admin-content-area {
            flex-grow: 1;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #fff;
            box-shadow: 0 0 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
            overflow-y: auto;
        }

        .admin-content-area h2 {
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        /* Fin de los estilos del Panel de Administraci√≥n */
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    {% include 'header.html.twig' %}

    {# Contenedor principal para el panel de administraci√≥n #}
    <div class="admin-main-container">
        {# Panel lateral de navegaci√≥n #}
        <aside class="admin-sidebar">
            <h2><i class="fas fa-cogs"></i> Admin Panel</h2>
            <nav>
                <ul>
                    <li><a href="/admin/users" class="nav-link {% if active_component == 'usuarioAdmin' %}active{% endif %}"><i class="fas fa-users"></i> Usuarios</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/admin/animales" class="nav-link {% if active_component == 'animalAdmin' %}active{% endif %}"><i class="fas fa-paw"></i> Animales</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/admin/noticias" class="nav-link {% if active_component == 'noticiaAdmin' %}active{% endif %}"><i class="fas fa-newspaper"></i> Noticias</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/admin/foro" class="nav-link {% if active_component == 'foroAdmin' %}active{% endif %}"><i class="fas fa-comments"></i> Foros</a></li>
                </ul>
            </nav>
        </aside>

        {# √Årea de contenido principal #}
        <main class="admin-content-area">
            {# Muestra el mensaje recibido desde el controlador #}
            {% if content_message is defined and content_message is not empty %}
                <div class="alert alert-primary" role="alert">
                    <h4 class="alert-heading">Info:</h4>
                    <p>{{ content_message }}</p>
                    <hr>
                    <p class="mb-0">Aqu√≠ ver√°s el contenido detallado de esta secci√≥n una vez se integren las llamadas a la API.</p>
                </div>
            {% else %}
                {# Contenido por defecto si no hay mensaje (ej. al cargar /admin por primera vez) #}
                <h2><i class="fas fa-tachometer-alt"></i> Dashboard Administrativo</h2>
                <p>Bienvenido al panel de administraci√≥n de MyZoo. Utiliza el men√∫ de la izquierda para navegar por las diferentes secciones de gesti√≥n.</p>
                <div class="alert alert-info mt-4" role="alert">
                    Este es tu espacio de trabajo principal.
                </div>
            {% endif %}
        </main>
    </div>

    {% include 'footer.html.twig' %}

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"
                integrity="sha384-geWF76RCwLtnZ8qwWowPQNguL3RmwHVBC9FhGdlKrxdiJJigb/j/68SIy3Te4Bkz"
                crossorigin="anonymous"></script>

    <script>
        window.ChatWidgetConfig = {
            webhook: {
                url: 'http://localhost:5678/webhook/f406671e-c954-4691-b39a-66c90aa2f103/chat',
                route: 'general'
            },
            branding: {
                logo: 'https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcQPSJrGEYze4X7nk28BHpXE_XlAoeg_vmwynQ&s',
                name: 'Zoo',
                welcomeText: '¬°Hola! ü¶Åüêµ ¬øEn qu√© puedo ayudarte hoy?',
                responseTimeText: 'Respondemos en pocos minutos ‚è≥'
            },
            style: {
                primaryColor: '#4CAF50',
                secondaryColor: '#2E7D32',
                position: 'right',
                backgroundColor: '#FAF3E0',
                fontColor: '#3E2723',
                borderRadius: '15px',
                buttonShadow: '0px 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2)',
                chatBubbleColor: '#A5D6A7',
                chatBubbleTextColor: '#1B5E20',
                fontFamily: '"Poppins", sans-serif'
            }
        };
    </script>
    <script src="https://nocodeveloper.com/chat.js"></script>

    {# No necesitamos admin.js si no hay carga din√°mica de componentes #}
    {% block javascripts %}{% endblock %}
</body>
</html>